short_text_with_quiz.text_japanese: 山田さんは去年、新しい街に引っ越しました。最初は一人ぼっちで、新しい環境に慣れるのに苦労しましたが、徐々に慣れてきました。今年は仕事で大きな挑戦がありました。大変でしたが、一生懸命戦い、最終的に成功しました。達成感を強く感じ、忘れられない経験となりました。めったに映画を見なくなりました。成長を実感しています。
short_text_with_quiz.text_english: Yamada-san moved to a new city last year.  At first, he felt lonely and struggled to adapt to his new environment, but he gradually got used to it.  This year, he faced a big challenge at work.  Even though it was difficult, he fought hard and ultimately achieved success.  He felt a deep sense of accomplishment, a feeling he'll never forget.  He rarely watches movies now, because he is too busy. He is very happy with his growth.

song_lyrics.lyrics_japanese:
学校はもう卒業　もう大人になった
新しい感覚感じる　違う感じ
学校の戦いには慣れたけど　これはまた違う
これまでの成長に感謝を感じる

たとえ辛い戦いがあっても
全力で戦う　それが理想

感心と感謝が入り混じる気持ち
支えてくれたみんなに

この感じ　これが成長

思想は構成され　考えは明確
達成感を感じる今
感動を覚えるほどの進歩
これからも戦い続ける　成長は止まらない

どんな困難があっても　この成功感は新しい
成功と努力の連想は明確
もう大人だけど　世界は大きく　理想も大きい
賛成　これからも戦う　未来は自分のものだから

感謝の気持ち胸に　新たに始める
この成長　この感じは　私の指針
理想に向かって頑張る
成功を願って　全てに挑む
song_lyrics.lyrics_english_translation:
The school days are over, now I'm an adult
I feel a new sensation, a different feeling
Though I'm used to the school battles, this is new
I feel gratitude for my growth so far

Even if there are difficult battles ahead
I'll fight with all my might, that's my ideal
Imagining success, I'll face the voting
Hoping my results show my growth

My feelings are a mix of admiration and thanks
For those who helped me along the way
I hardly ever felt such deep emotion before
This feeling, this is my growth

My thoughts are organized, my ideas are clear
I feel a sense of accomplishment now
I'm deeply moved by my progress
I'll keep fighting, my growth never ends

No matter the difficulty, this feeling of success is new
The association between success and effort is clear
Though I'm an adult now, the world is huge, and so are my ideals
I agree to fight on, for my future is my own

With my thanks in my heart, I start anew
This growth, this feeling is my guiding star
I'll strive towards my ideals
Hoping for success in everything I do
song_lyrics.song_title: 成長の戦い (Seichō no Tatakai) - The Battle of Growth
